1845
03:38:42,955 --> 03:38:45,041
It would've been her.

1846
03:38:57,219 --> 03:39:00,389
I'm glad to be with you,
Samwise Gamgee...

1847
03:39:04,685 --> 03:39:07,605
...here at the end of all things.

1848
03:39:30,626 --> 03:39:41,115
<i><font color="#008000">♫ Orthannen im vi ól</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(In a dream I was lifted up)</font></i>

1849
03:39:41,626 --> 03:39:44,115
<i><font color="#008000">♫ Coll e dû</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(Borne from the darkness)</font></i>

1850
03:39:44,626 --> 03:40:00,115
<i><font color="#008000">♫ Na rovail mae sui</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(on wings soft as the wind)</font></i>

1851
03:40:00,626 --> 03:40:08,115
<i><font color="#008000">♫ Man prestant i ardhon?</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(What's happened to the world?)</font></i>

1852
03:40:08,626 --> 03:40:23,115
<i><font color="#008000">♫ Cerithar aen dim úthenin?</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(Is everything sad going to come untrue?)</font></i>

1853
